General.Name: Icares Medicus Inc
General.Description: ICARES Medicus, Inc., a nano-medical material company, focuses on the research and development, manufacture, and sale of ophthalmic medical materials in Taiwan and internationally. It provides ophthalmic medical materials, including intraocular lens for the treatment of cataract, myopia, hyperopia, presbyopia, or astigmatism; and surgical implantation systems, as well as related technical services. ICARES Medicus, Inc. was incorporated in 2011 and is based in Zhubei, Taiwan.
